# 📊 Fraud Detection Workflow

```text
User Initiates Transaction
            ↓
AI Fraud Analysis
            ↓
 ┌───────────────────┐
 │ Safe Transaction  │
 └───────────────────┘
            ↓
         SUCCESS

            OR

 ┌───────────────────┐
 │ Suspicious        │
 └───────────────────┘
            ↓
      Email OTP
            ↓
      OTP Verify
            ↓
         SUCCESS

            OR

 ┌───────────────────┐
 │ Fraud Detected    │
 └───────────────────┘
            ↓
         BLOCKED
```

